ank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/chinese-tycoon-holed-up-in-manhattan-hotel-is-accused-of-spying-for-beijing-11563810726</a><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再信佢d風喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:20:27.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWSJ只係報導有人指控佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725b84b3713956cfbc1a8f908d5c8f9ec307cc35","tid":1351650,"uid":186704,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:22:41.000Z","msg":"But a Washington-area research firm in a commercial dispute with Mr. Guo alleged in a Friday federal court counterclaim that he is a spy for the Chinese government.<br />\n<br />\nfirm名又冇 , 又唔係政府告 , 純單方面指控"},{"pid":"67b9e3257882d6abbf5da54f4ee63574cff38bd6","tid":1351650,"uid":260428,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:23:27.000Z","msg":"一直無人信架啦"},{"pid":"973ea0e3896388951196d00a4fc32155bdba7ba2","tid":1351650,"uid":94484,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:23:49.000Z","msg":"一日冇冰冰圖<br />\n一日都唔信佢"},{"pid":"32025bb5936627d7db80e84729fcbf6d67797667","tid":1351650,"uid":147467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3772f76ff28dc028b1e74fce1eef012354e3406b","tid":1351650,"uid":184679,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"cbb2b41bc8674ac6935e100a679b299d7b008b45","tid":1351650,"uid":147467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:00:10.000Z","msg":"Chinese Tycoon Holed Up in Manhattan Hotel Is Accused of Spying <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/chinese-tycoon-holed-up-in-manhattan-hotel-is-accused-of-spying-for-beijing-11563810726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fchinese-tycoon-holed-up-in-manhattan-hotel-is-accused-of-spying-for-beijing-11563810726&d=YNGzf4wH3lBRdiFquXkn2wAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=d5b9e35b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/chinese-tycoon-holed-up-in-manhattan-hotel-is-accused-of-spying-for-beijing-11563810726</a><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再信佢d風喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:20:27.000Z","msg":"標題黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWSJ只係報導有人指控佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"係 但WSJ報得始終都有D ground<br />\n主要個allegations就係下面呢D<br />\n//Strategic Vision enlisted investigators who are former intelligence or law-enforcement personnel to perform the research, according to Friday&rsquo;s filing. The filing said investigators determined the first 15 names provided by Mr. Guo had been designated by the U.S. as &ldquo;Records Protected&rdquo; individuals, for whom certain information wasn&rsquo;t subject to disclosure. Such a designation is used in highly classified and access-restricted government databases, former intelligence officials said. The immigration status about such designees is often blocked in restricted government databases, and can suggest the person may be a foreigner who is assisting the U.S. government, experts said.<br />\n<br />\nStrategic Vision said it concluded Mr. Guo was seeking information on Chinese nationals who may have been helping the U.S. government in national-security investigations or who were involved in other sensitive matters, according to the filing.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Guo never intended to use the fruits of Strategic Vision&rsquo;s research against the Chinese Communist Party,&rdquo; the court filing said. &ldquo;That is because Guo was not the dissident he claimed to be. Instead, Guo Wengui was, and is, a dissident-hunter, propagandist, and agent in the service of the People&rsquo;s Republic of China and the Chinese Communist Party.&rdquo; //<br />\n<br />\n//Mr. Guo also has tried to use his money and allies such as Mr. Bannon to influence two interlinked groups in Washington that favor a tough stance toward China, Strategic Vision alleged in the filing. The company said this is further evidence that Mr. Guo is working for the Chinese Communist Party&mdash;not against it.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to the filing, a group led by Messrs. Guo and Bannon allegedly discussed ways to provide &ldquo;large amounts&rdquo; of money to the Center for Security Policy&mdash;a conservative Washington think tank&mdash;and the newly formed &ldquo;Committee on the Present Danger: China&rdquo; that the center backs. Some people at the think tank viewed it as an attempt by Mr. Guo to take over the anti-China committee, the filing said.//<br />\n<br />\n自己判斷下 當然可能有D係冇咁convincing 但第一段如果有evidence其實算幾強嘅"},{"pid":"cf727edff5b1bf07e52fa9997d778ccbdc4e904d","tid":1351650,"uid":147467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49ef930f7e35171ed245273f3d2d7bace80839b","tid":1351650,"uid":147467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84bf682033aea28d6c3c13aac0ad8f7067c1f9a","tid":1351650,"uid":147467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1364ce6e34952d5ee520db79e0cf124aef75a406","tid":1351650,"uid":131282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T17:42:10.000Z","msg":"👻"},{"pid":"1bbdda9c8f310066e51acb4d68af8b28085cdfb7","tid":1351650,"uid":147467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T23:12:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d715c35e7ab304f0bab80dcb90e0e1831fee64d","tid"